They can't lie their way out of it! Biden promised to end the virus, hasn't done it. Psaki blames Trump, but they've failed based on their own metrics, Buck notes.. Second U.S Omicron case confirmed. Clay says only reason they stopped talking about record-high hospitalizations is because they're not occurring in red states anymore. Senator Cruz joins us, torches Fauci, vax mandates and the NBA. Sick, dark-hearted liberals celebrate abortions.
